    "date": "2019-08-05T18:05:53Z",
    "text": "Ensuring Patient Access to Critical Breakthrough Products Act of 2018\n\nThis bill (1) allows designated medical breakthrough devices to be temporarily covered under Medicare during a specified transitional period, (2) establishes a process to allow for continued coverage after the transitional period has expired, and (3) modifies other Medicare payment systems relating to new medical technology."
